## terraform commands ##

# terraform init 
# terraform fmt
# terraform valdiate
# terraform plan
# terraform apply --auto-approve
# terraform destroy
# terraform state show _________ for example = aws_internet_gateway.gw OR aws_vpc.lab-vpc
# terraform destroy -target aws_instance.my-ec2-instance  # delete specific resource


